commitResults.messageTitle: Change retrieval of projects to getProject
commitResults.messageBody:
Change retrieval of projects from getProjectList().get to getProject.

getNumberOfProjects() returns number of projects in project list.

Before the switch statements, we use a regex to detect slashes. It will break phrases up based on slashes into key-value pairs in a hashmap. So example "task n/play guitar d/2020": n is the key and play guitar the value. d is the key and 2020 the value.
